com.robindrew.common.io.data

Interface IDataWriter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.io.DataOutput
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ByteArrayDataWriter, DataWriter

    public interface IDataWriter
extends java.io.DataOutput, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    The Data Set Input interface provides advanced stream reading capabilities.
